				<h3 class="listing">Recognition Type</h3>
				<p><span id="ContentPlaceHolderDefault_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_PlacePage1_lblRecognitionType">National Historic Site of Canada</span></p>
				
